snippet.textDisplay:
Guessing the plot (having no prior knowledge of the lore other than "hey look, that's Wonder Woman!"):

1. Big business dude invented a machine that can "grant wishes," but really makes some sort of half illusion / half reality projection that only lasts as long as the machine is on, and eventually it grows too powerful and must be destroyed (Steve will sacrifice himself a second time of course).
2. Kristin Wiig / Cheetah is a carbon copy of Guy Pearce / Aldridge Killian from Iron Man 3, being the dork who adores our hero at the beginning (with lesbian undertones here), but then is spurned and goes on to become a hottie with a taste for vengeance. Cheetah will get her hotness and superpowers from the wish machine and thus will try to stop WW and Steve from destroying it.
